pull_request.title: Revert "Enabling NTRU by default, minor cleaning of configure.ac"
pull_request.body:
Reverts open-quantum-safe/liboqs#142

clang-format in brew has been updated very recently and apparently this has changed how it formats things **again**.  This is not the first time we've run into problems with clang-format inconsistencies.  I am not sure how to ensure reliable formatting behaviour across platforms and clang-format versions.
